column27: This report summarizes performance for 350 orders across multiple regions, countries, and product categories.
Overall revenue for the period is approximately 22.46M, with an average profit per order of about 14.48K.
Average units sold per order is around 256 units, indicating relatively large order sizes across the dataset.
Regional analysis shows revenue distributed across East, West, North, and an Unknown region, with total revenue by region and category already summarized in the cross-tab area (U:X).
The dashboard metrics in Y2:Y5 and Z2:Z5 provide a quick view of total revenue, average profit, total orders, and average units sold per order for ongoing monitoring.
